  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nWith SPX at 6767 sitting right between the max negative gamma at 6750 (-49.5B) and positive gamma wall at 6800 (+41.3B), dealers are currently in buy mode after the recent wall break through 6750, creating amplifying flows that should continue pushing price higher toward the 6800 resistance. The breakout regime with massive negative GEX concentration from 6750-6765 means any dips will be aggressively bought by dealers while rallies get sold into the 6800+ zone. Watch 6800 as the critical flip point - a break above turns dealers from sellers back to buyers, while failure here sets up violent selling pressure back through the negative gamma minefield below.\n\n**Bottom line:** expect volatile push higher toward 6800 with strong dealer buying support on any pullbacks to 6750.",
